    <div class="clearfix colelem" id="u359-4"><!-- content -->
     <p>Nicole and her friends are at a Chantilly football game. The stadium is running a promotion where a slice of pizza are $1.50 each. Suppose d represents the number of pizza slices Nicole and her friends eat. Then 1.50d represents the total cost of&nbsp; pizza slices eaten.</p>
